headline.main: STATEMENTS ON DISPUTE; Davis, Reuter and London OWI Discuss Cairo Release

lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON, Dec. 2 (AP) -- Following is an Office of War Information paraphase of the cable sent Nov. 30 by Elmer Davis, OWI Director, to Brendan Bracken, British Minister of Information:
abstract: Davis confirms protest to Bracken; protest and Reuter statement texts; Bracken questioned on news leak, Commons; Amer Newspaper Eds Soc protests conf news handling
